                <p>CFOs and Chief Technology Officers should benchmark internal AI workload costs against Alibaba's 30 percent AI penetration metric before the end of Q2. If your AI spend as a percentage of total cloud is materially below that figure, audit whether current providers are delivering competitive AI model access or whether procurement should open Alibaba Cloud and local hyperscaler RFPs by Q3.</p>
